headline: Western Digital's Q2 Earnings on Deck: Is the Stock Worth Buying Now?
summary: WDC sees fiscal Q2 2026 non-GAAP revenue of $2.9B, up 20% year over year, as data center demand and high-capacity drives support growth momentum.

headline: NetApp Data Platform Powers Data Operations for Super Bowl LX
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., January 27, 2026--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the Intelligent Data Infrastructure company, today announced that it is powering data operations for Super Bowl LX.
